const c=e=>{switch(e){case"vehicle":return"Vehicle";case"property":return"Property";default:return"Asset"}},m=e=>{switch(e){case"vehicle":return"Vehicle VIN";case"property":return"Property ID";default:return"Asset ID"}},u=e=>{if(e.Remaining>0){const t=(100+e.InterestRate)/100;return Math.ceil(e.Remaining*t)}else return 0},a=(e,t=1)=>{if(e.Remaining>0){const s=(100+e.InterestRate)/100,n=e.TotalPayments-e.PaidPayments;e.MissedPayments>1&&t===1&&(t=e.MissedPayments),t>n&&(t=n);const i=e.Remaining/n*t*s;return Math.ceil(i)}else return 0};export{c as a,a as b,m as c,u as g};
